<emphasis id="B9760756FFEB5626FD5CD484FF6803D8" box="[743,771,1172,1193]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="33">(8)</emphasis>
Left wing. 
<emphasis id="B9760756FFEB5626FCC8D484FFE403D8" box="[883,911,1172,1193]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="33">(9)</emphasis>
Distal part of aedeagus, scale = 0.3 mm. 
<emphasis id="B9760756FFEB5626FAA6D484F92E03D8" box="[1309,1349,1172,1193]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="33">(10)</emphasis>
Right arista (basal segmentation unclear). 
<emphasis id="B9760756FFEB5626FE7BD4BEFDB303B2" box="[448,472,1198,1219]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="33">bu</emphasis>
